## 12) Your EC2 instance is reachable through SSH, but the application is not opening in browser. How do you troubleshoot?

**Answer:**\
I check step by step:

1.  is application process running?\

```{=html}
<!-- -->
```
    ps -ef | grep app
    systemctl status nginx

2.  is app listening on expected port?\

```{=html}
<!-- -->
```
    ss -tulpn

3.  is security group allowing traffic?\
4.  is reverse proxy config correct?\
5.  are logs showing startup or runtime errors?\
6.  is disk full?\
7.  is app bound to localhost only?

This lets me isolate whether the issue is process, port, proxy,
firewall, or application config.

