## 18) A shell script used in deployment works manually, but fails in Jenkins. Why?

**Answer:**\
Common reasons:

-   different user permissions\
-   environment variables missing in Jenkins\
-   path differences\
-   shell differences\
-   credentials not available\
-   working directory mismatch

